{"tid":2236434,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"vivo概念機取消無謂前鏡頭的可拆卸前置鏡頭模塊獲紅點設計獎","createTime":"2020-10-09T12:42:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T11:05:39.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5b91bd64803dbe577714bb9066e6841b927989b9","tid":2236434,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T12:42:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://feng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com/2020/10/09/193432lszwpj9a1btq2j1d.png?imageMogr2/format/jpg/interlace/0/quality/100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffeng-bbs-att-1255531212.image.myqcloud.com%2F2020%2F10%2F09%2F193432lszwpj9a1btq2j1d.png%3FimageMogr2%2Fformat%2Fjpg%2Finterlace%2F0%2Fquality%2F100&h=8972a975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n製造商一直在嘗試進行一些設計更改，以使其設備在競爭中脫穎而出。從彈出式攝像頭到屏下攝像頭，前置攝像頭模塊正在發生重大的發展。<br />\nimage<br />\n最近，vivo 開發了一款名為 IFEA 的新概念智能電話，該機具有可拆卸的前置攝像頭模塊。現在，該模塊化設計贏得了紅點設計概念大獎。<br />\n<br />\n根據獎項登陸頁面上的描述，vivo 這款新的IFEA智能設計旨在提供一種新的攝影系統和體驗，與普通智能電話所提供的完全不同。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nIFEA 旨在為智能手機配備可拆卸的前置攝像頭。它集成了增強的拍攝功能，用戶可以隨時隨地創建和錄製圖像和視頻。<br />\n<br />\n此外，還可以通過語音命令來控制該設備，這被稱為交互式的直觀設計。IFEA 具有多種附件和不同模式的支撐機構，以增加穩定性和存儲。<br />\n<br />\n到目前為止，這款手機似乎只是一個概念設計，該公司還沒有計劃很快將其投入商業使用。"},{"pid":"2c79031711a471c4005db48434da3acd2d232aec","tid":2236434,"uid":35429,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"Sony Ericsson T68i: Am I a joke to you?<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Q6eDcNnJ4pA/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FQ6eDcNnJ4pA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=61bbb1ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"748aee0afd553d813770381ca8ad90a33f2bd7cd","tid":2236434,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"咁似 LG G5 啲 friend"},{"pid":"0558ef3590f5eb1bc11404270d059dea4b80951c","tid":2236434,"uid":39182,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T13:03:52.00